</style></div><div data-rid="64c6588d-fdad-411d-ae7a-7edc1c2fcbe7" class="r-u7ufq"><div data-rid="50284a9b-a125-4750-a36e-2b51b693ad00" class="r-1xq9b75"><div data-rid="1e230d83-4a00-43d8-9e44-e7bf4a52c325" class="r-10uqp7y"><div data-rid="e610b8a3-6179-46bd-8e47-bac62970bba6" class="r-n3qu2w"><div data-rid="1bd4e3f0-d13e-4e94-8069-f644c52dc45a" class="r-xlpmon"><div data-rid="24c34224-7717-4ba5-af04-2521979c4a98" class="r-dedjsh"><div data-rid="2111c67e-87f6-4914-9462-f9c3b466eb32" class="r-hv3jbf"><div data-rid="efa27895-c256-4cc9-bb71-406382d81008" class="r-1nybz37"><div data-rid="d889f756-43be-45ba-b7b3-d16b9379f8bb" class="r-dhpfv1"><div data-rid="83a9e973-01a9-4e78-b939-36f74648384b" class="r-13pt10y"><div data-rid="2b66b313-f735-4695-a189-658cc72c8eba" class="r-1rz8paw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>5 Reasons Blume’s Clear Skin Kit is a Must Have to Beat Hormonal Acne (Especially if you have Sensitive Skin)</strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="6bd48b15-be61-48ba-9968-e81df222b1e8" class="r-1tsbfzh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Acne treatment shouldn’t mean sacrificing your skin’s health and comfort. Blume’s Clear Skin</p><p>Kit offers a gentle, effective solution that understands your skin’s unique needs—giving you<span style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration-line: inherit; text-transform: inherit; background-color: transparent;">clear skin without the harsh side effects. Here’s why Blume’s Clear Skin Kit is perfect for&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration-line: inherit; text-transform: inherit; background-color: transparent;">tackling hormonal acne while being kind to sensitive skin.</span></p><p></p></span></div><picture data-rid="ecaf6218-183b-4ced-a417-74d6a8364888" class="r-1inyyqf"><source srcSet="https://www.blume.com/cdn/shop/files/s2677870-av-07_02c0befe-052e-4150-a0f4-4d24f2abd3e8_1200x.png?v=1769119224&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://www.blume.com/cdn/shop/files/s2677870-av-07_02c0befe-052e-4150-a0f4-4d24f2abd3e8_1200x.png?v=1769119224&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://www.blume.com/cdn/shop/files/s2677870-av-07_02c0befe-052e-4150-a0f4-4d24f2abd3e8_1200x.png?v=1769119224&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://www.blume.com/cdn/shop/files/s2677870-av-07_02c0befe-052e-4150-a0f4-4d24f2abd3e8_1200x.png?v=1769119224" alt="Blue skincare products with disco balls and red background." class="r-16o38g" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div><div data-rid="dc469abe-d13e-4da9-b192-65890d7894c7" class="r-14phxhl"><div data-rid="c5de32fd-b11e-408f-8fe2-32d85e0e5aa3" class="r-r3qbhu"><div data-rid="9ebf5f84-f235-4a43-b8db-490ba5af17f0" class="r-1pdevbf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>1. Treat Hormonal Acne Without the Harsh Side Effects</p></span></div><div data-rid="8d8acd01-c636-4436-bd2c-921ac85cd61c" class="r-a19pz1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Tired of acne treatments that don't work on hormonal acne? Most acne treatments sit on the surface and don't actually penetrate below the top layer. Plus they strip your skin, leaving it red, dry, and more irritated than before. Blume’s Clear Skin Kit takes a different approach: it combines powerful, natural ingredients that target hormonal acne without compromising your skin’s health. No harshness, just calm, clear skin that feels as good as it looks.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="a883e684-c1b3-4e0a-8386-33b231a3c4b0" class="r-chwwjy"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/2_dd176fad-2d50-4a84-b48e-68ed6a4e7aea.png?v=1732078664" alt="Side-by-side comparison of skin before and after treatment, showing significant improvement." class="r-kvqt8f" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="f4fb8738-f8c7-43c8-91fc-cdfe228599d7" class="r-xy4bw3"><div data-rid="3f1ec30c-856d-41e3-bc38-1d6db2dede43" class="r-1895q05"><div data-rid="b0dd0ff9-e7bf-4a26-9d40-fa7cc0172f87" class="r-1gz6jf0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>2. A Simple Routine You’ll Actually Stick To</p></span></div><div data-rid="da35d1bc-83ac-4827-b0fd-dd23fd1d459f" class="r-a2euq7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Say goodbye to complicated skincare routines. With just three easy steps, the Blume kit keeps it quick, effective, and stress-free. You’ll have clear, balanced skin without the hassle of a 10-step process. Plus Blume’s formula fights the root causes of acne while soothing your skin. It’s designed to treat and prevent future breakouts.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="c1db6d8d-9e36-448e-b404-51aff275b179" class="r-yjoqjj"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/3_5258d4e4-3a70-49e3-96f6-13af736caed3.png?v=1732078664" alt="Skincare products and accessories on a white bathroom counter." class="r-17kpotp" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="ffcc2394-d784-46b2-8765-22454af77f7d" class="r-13xooal"><div data-rid="4d460787-4f96-4c00-84ba-cd47b3011133" class="r-vuuhrl"><div data-rid="d41af9bb-8fb5-4273-935d-f2b6557c72a7" class="r-17vlh5h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>3. Supports Your Skin’s Natural Barrier</p></span></div><div data-rid="b7c31d1f-4daa-4992-8060-ad61a005bd7b" class="r-iccu9t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Sensitive skin is often prone to redness and irritation, especially with acne treatments that strip away moisture. Blume’s Clear Skin Kit helps reinforce your skin’s natural barrier, protecting it from dryness and environmental stressors. This means your skin stays strong, resilient, and less reactive, even while fighting acne.</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="148bf157-4d87-453f-8c99-57fa33172425" class="r-1v6acx5"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/4_7374d342-4352-4664-b3d7-77661ba34546.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/4_7374d342-4352-4664-b3d7-77661ba34546.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/4_7374d342-4352-4664-b3d7-77661ba34546.png?v=1732078664&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/4_7374d342-4352-4664-b3d7-77661ba34546.png?v=1732078664" alt="Close-up of skincare cream with text about ceramides and amino acids." class="r-hjirtd" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="adb73169-6d06-4add-bff5-4038d8d34a03" class="r-1u21erm"><div data-rid="aa8c56a3-77a8-486a-8609-65df3b5448c1" class="r-1v76ab3"><div data-rid="b6d2d2f4-6738-4fda-a9dc-c1ed5196aaa9" class="r-55bu5l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>4. Loved by Thousands with Hormonal Acne</p></span></div><div data-rid="263aa692-7c31-457f-838e-53932b6118d3" class="r-1k53813 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Don’t just take our word for it—thousands of users with hormonal acne and sensitive skin rave about their results with Blume. With over 5,000 5-star reviews, join the community of over 500,000 clear-skin believers who’ve finally found a routine that truly works!</p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="5ac0b8b3-3604-4441-9321-3556c7ae423f" class="r-e5iz7f"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/5_406d3b1d-499a-4b45-b120-02b8e0c1461b.png?v=1732078665&amp;width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/5_406d3b1d-499a-4b45-b120-02b8e0c1461b.png?v=1732078665&amp;width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/5_406d3b1d-499a-4b45-b120-02b8e0c1461b.png?v=1732078665&amp;width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0003/4580/0755/files/5_406d3b1d-499a-4b45-b120-02b8e0c1461b.png?v=1732078665" alt="Before-and-after acne treatment progress over several months on different individuals." class="r-1bvtw9e" loading="lazy"/></picture></div><div data-rid="d2772199-94fd-4b2a-a217-9c6050cc984e" class="r-19i1chy"><div data-rid="bb99f0a1-4538-48f3-bc8c-49711fd1bea4" class="r-1win0f0"><div data-rid="b1ba5dab-ccdf-4932-9656-377bf6b4ba28" class="r-13i9amg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When it comes to acne, you shouldn’t have to choose between effectiveness and gentleness. The Clear Skin Kit is formulated with a blend of soothing plant-based ingredients and acne-fighting ingredients that deliver real results without the irritation. I